I just read a book written by a bible scholar and Baptist minister that was an interesting exploration of some of the issues brought up in this thread. It's called &quot;Rescuing Jesus from the Christians.&quot; He shows that Jesus was a mistaken prophet (the &quot;kingdom&quot; never came) and that Christians have both aggrandized and sentimentalized him far beyond what anything in the bible can support. It was fascinating reading.<br>
